Visit www.greatnonprofits.org to read independent reviews of Bais Chana written by alumnae, staff, volunteers and donors. Bais Chana Women International is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit.

DONATE

JEWISH UNCAMP is a project of Bais Chana Women International a Chabad nonprofit organization that serves an international clientele of Jewish women from all walks of life, ages 15 and up, with Jewish education, enrichment and support.

Our programs include Jewish UnCamp for teen girls 16-19, Snorkel & Study and Sun&Study for college women, Jewish Learning Retreats for Women of all Ages and Single Jewish Moms Connect. Rabbi Manis Friedman leads a team of A-List Jewish educators and mentors at every program.
